  <brief_title>Surgery or Clincial Follow up, in Patients With Bell' s Palsy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Surgery or Clinical Follow-up in Patients With Bell's Palsy. A Prospective, Parallell, Single Center, Randomized , Open Surgery Clinical Study.</official_title>
