  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate if an early surgical intervention on patienst
      with Bell´s Palsy has a better impact on their facial muscular function and their quality of
      life as compared to conventional therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
